==========================MODEL EXPLAINATION==========================

The User will Select 

(1) The Course, 
then the Departments will be sorted on the basis of the Course.

(2) The Department,
then the Semesters will be sorted on the basis of the Course & Department.

(3) The Semesters,
then the Subjects will be sorted on the basis of the Course, Department and Semester.

(4) The Subjects,
then the books will be sorted on the basis of the Course, Department, Semester, and Subject.